From: Jianfeng Liu <Jianfeng.Liu@cixtech.com>
Date: Wed, 18 Mar 2026 14:29:41 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 464/582] CIXTECH: clk: clkdev: increase clkdev MAX_CON_ID from
 16 to 32

Signed-off-by: Jianfeng Liu <Jianfeng.Liu@cixtech.com>

Link: https://github.com/cixtech/cix-linux-main/tree/3b621ea88d4caaec9b0dd763600dbb8cabb71653
Signed-off-by: Mingcong Bai <jeffbai@aosc.io>
---
 drivers/clk/clkdev.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/clk/clkdev.c b/drivers/clk/clkdev.c
index abaa0f9e0083..6fbcdbc849e5 100644
--- a/drivers/clk/clkdev.c
+++ b/drivers/clk/clkdev.c
@@ -145,7 +145,7 @@ void clkdev_add_table(struct clk_lookup *cl, size_t num)
 }
 
 #define MAX_DEV_ID	24
-#define MAX_CON_ID	16
+#define MAX_CON_ID	32
 
 struct clk_lookup_alloc {
 	struct clk_lookup cl;
